data.eml:eml: Two new genera of Australian dung beetles (Coleoptera: Scarabaeidae: Scarabaeinae) with the description of six new species and transfer of six described species

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Gunter, Nicole L., Weir, Thomas A. (2017): Two new genera of Australian dung beetles (Coleoptera: Scarabaeidae: Scarabaeinae) with the description of six new species and transfer of six described species. Zootaxa 4290 (2): 201-243, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4290.2.1
